It's just a job he gives
to all the young bucks

26:49.120 --> 26:52.680
whenever he goes away, justto remind them I'm his.

26:52.800 --> 26:54.760
Well, what makes you his?

26:54.880 --> 26:58.000
The rock on your finger?

26:58.120 --> 27:01.080
Yeah, it kind of does.

27:01.200 --> 27:02.920
Mind you, without an
actual wedding date

27:03.040 --> 27:06.840
to go with it, where's
the line between fiance

27:06.960 --> 27:09.440
and a mistress with a ring?

27:09.560 --> 27:11.600
Why wouldn't he marry you?

27:11.720 --> 27:13.240
Because Evan gets bored.

27:13.360 --> 27:15.240
Because he likes collectingbeautiful things.

27:15.360 --> 27:18.640
Because his desire tostay eternally young means

27:18.760 --> 27:20.520
a have a "use by" date.

27:20.640 --> 27:23.560
And I am telling
you way too much.

27:23.680 --> 27:26.160
You have far too
much over me now.

27:26.280 --> 27:28.560
So tell me your
deepest, darkest secret.

27:28.680 --> 27:29.440
Now.

27:35.360 --> 27:36.480
I shot a man.

27:36.600 --> 27:37.400
Bullshit.

27:44.640 --> 27:47.080
Did he die?

27:47.200 --> 27:49.000
No.

27:49.120 --> 27:52.080
Did you go to prison?

27:52.200 --> 27:53.320
No.

27:53.440 --> 27:54.240
Why'd you shoot him?

27:58.720 --> 28:00.720
I was protecting someone.

28:00.840 --> 28:01.600
A woman?

28:04.880 --> 28:07.160
I'm going to go to bed.

28:07.280 --> 28:08.040
Thanks for the cards.

28:41.160 --> 28:44.040
[moaning]

28:49.680 --> 28:51.560
Now we've both got secrets.

29:04.160 --> 29:07.560
[music playing]

29:10.160 --> 29:11.520
Man.

29:11.640 --> 29:13.160
After last night, when Iwas faced with certain death

29:13.280 --> 29:16.120
at the hands of angry Dallies,I thought my life of crime

29:16.240 --> 29:17.680
was over.

29:17.800 --> 29:20.640
If you're so certain,how come you're here today?

29:20.760 --> 29:24.600
Luckily, I was only a cog
in someone else's wheel.

29:24.720 --> 29:25.560
Yep.

29:25.680 --> 29:27.760
That'll do the trick.

29:27.880 --> 29:29.800
It was an honor to
steal her for you--

29:29.920 --> 29:31.280
the tow truck, I mean.

29:31.400 --> 29:33.400
They cause so much
hardship to my people.

29:33.520 --> 29:36.480
So there's some
poetic justice here.

29:36.600 --> 29:38.800
Also, there was this.

29:38.920 --> 29:39.920
BERT: Did you get the car?

29:40.040 --> 29:40.960
Yep.

29:41.080 --> 29:43.000
Did you park it where I asked?

29:43.120 --> 29:44.640
Everything is
as you requested.

29:53.680 --> 29:54.440
You need to go.

29:54.560 --> 29:55.960
He'll be back soon.

29:56.080 --> 29:57.200
What about what
happened last--

29:57.320 --> 30:00.120
[shushes] Nothing
happened last night.

30:11.160 --> 30:12.600
Hey!

30:12.720 --> 30:14.200
Where the fuck you been?

30:14.320 --> 30:15.400
I wait for you all night!

30:15.520 --> 30:16.880
You make me sleep
in my fucking car!

30:17.000 --> 30:18.000
Oh, for God's sake.

30:18.120 --> 30:19.480
What now?

30:19.600 --> 30:21.520
Don't you take the nameof our lord in vain with me.

30:21.640 --> 30:24.760
Without me, you'd be in jail
right now, Mr. Arsonist.

30:24.880 --> 30:26.240
I'm sure you and my
father have worked out

30:26.360 --> 30:27.440
some sort of punishment for me.

30:27.560 --> 30:30.440
Hey, your father
is a good man.

30:30.560 --> 30:32.320
What do you want?

30:32.440 --> 30:34.720
A business proposition.

30:40.960 --> 30:42.680
