you've been all night,

30:42.800 --> 30:44.440
but I'm pretty sure you
won't tell me the truth.

30:44.560 --> 30:45.360
Evan's house.

30:48.640 --> 30:50.200
So you're still
working for him then?

30:50.320 --> 30:52.440
Far as I know.

30:52.560 --> 30:54.840
Found that safe yet?

30:54.960 --> 30:56.280
Pretty sure it doesn't exist.

30:56.400 --> 30:57.360
It'll be there.

30:57.480 --> 30:58.960
Why?

30:59.080 --> 31:00.320
Because your friend who's neverbeen in the place says so.

31:00.440 --> 31:02.080
She knows her man, all right?

31:02.200 --> 31:03.240
It'll be there somewhere.

31:03.360 --> 31:04.600
Well, I can't
fucking find it, can I?

31:04.720 --> 31:09.160
Don't you speak to
your mother like that.

31:09.280 --> 31:10.600
[sighs]

31:10.720 --> 31:12.320
Is Dad here?

31:12.440 --> 31:14.320
He's at Lefty's,
lucky for you.

31:14.440 --> 31:16.000
And for Christ's sake,
stop winding him up.

31:16.120 --> 31:18.640
Every time you wind him up,I have to calm him back down.

31:18.760 --> 31:20.600
