bloody aggravation.

31:20.720 --> 31:24.440
And stay away from the Dalliestoo, if you can help it.

31:24.560 --> 31:27.080
Yeah, that's going tobe easier said than done.

31:27.200 --> 31:29.960
[doorbell rings]

31:32.000 --> 31:33.240
