anything in the paper

31:51.520 --> 31:53.920
today about a fire anywhere.

31:54.040 --> 31:55.040
There was a complication.

31:55.160 --> 31:56.120
I don't care about
complications.

31:56.240 --> 31:58.360
I just wanted the job done.

31:58.480 --> 32:01.240
It'll cost you 20 thou.

32:01.360 --> 32:02.680
Are you blackmailing me?

32:02.800 --> 32:03.800
Not me.

32:03.920 --> 32:05.560
And they don't see
it as blackmail.

32:05.680 --> 32:07.560
A business proposition.

32:07.680 --> 32:08.480
For me?

32:08.600 --> 32:09.760
I know who you work for.

32:09.880 --> 32:12.080
And we know what Mr. Lace wants.

32:12.200 --> 32:13.880
And he can have it.

32:14.000 --> 32:15.240
He can have building.

32:15.360 --> 32:16.920
Great.You-- you should tell him that!

32:17.040 --> 32:17.840
No!

32:17.960 --> 32:18.720
I tell you!

32:18.840 --> 32:20.120
And you tell him.

32:20.240 --> 32:21.840
There must be reparations.

32:21.960 --> 32:25.120
So they want $20,000
in reparations.

32:25.240 --> 32:28.080
The thing is, they want itin cash and they want it today.

32:28.200 --> 32:29.880
Otherwise, it goes
up to 30 thou.

32:30.000 --> 32:33.320
Those fucking Dally
gangster pricks.

32:33.440 --> 32:34.200
Fine.

32:34.320 --> 32:35.720
If that's what they want.

32:35.840 --> 32:36.840
Saves us burning
down this place.

32:36.960 --> 32:38.040
Uh, no.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.160
They want that too.

32:39.280 --> 32:41.480
[imitates flames]
Lucky my Uncle

32:41.600 --> 32:44.720
Rocky has very good insurance.

32:44.840 --> 32:48.560
It will look like
electrical fault, yes?

32:48.680 --> 32:50.360
Sure.

32:50.480 --> 32:52.280
Makes good business
sense, I suppose.

32:59.360 --> 33:00.160
Mate.

33:13.640 --> 33:14.400
Hey.

33:18.920 --> 33:19.720
Go.

33:19.840 --> 33:20.800
Make it so.

33:20.920 --> 33:21.920
Consider it done.

33:24.720 --> 33:26.760
Hey, good work with
Joanne, by the way.

33:26.880 --> 33:29.960
She told me you battered someperv in the bushes outside.

33:30.080 --> 33:31.000
Yeah.

33:31.120 --> 33:32.520
Yeah, it was nothing.
Really.

33:32.640 --> 33:33.440
Appreciate it.

33:33.560 --> 33:34.320
Thanks.

33:41.400 --> 33:43.320
Do you want my suggestion?

33:43.440 --> 33:44.800
Kick him out.

33:44.920 --> 33:47.440
Oddly tame at his age, solet the little prick learn

33:47.560 --> 33:49.600
about life the hard way,
without Mommy and Daddy

33:49.720 --> 33:50.600
to pick up the pieces.

33:50.720 --> 33:52.120
