33:52.240 --> 33:54.520
Rita's got too much of
a soft spot for the boy.

33:54.640 --> 33:55.920
LEFTY: Are you off, love?

33:56.040 --> 33:57.320
Uh, Jazzercise.

33:57.440 --> 33:58.400
