35:58.040 --> 35:59.040
You got a watch?

35:59.160 --> 35:59.920
Yeah.

36:00.040 --> 36:01.120
OK.

36:01.240 --> 36:02.640
You're in charge.

36:02.760 --> 36:03.520
Of what?

36:03.640 --> 36:04.400
You'll see.

36:09.040 --> 36:13.600
Have you tried sittingWolf down, talking to him?

36:13.720 --> 36:15.640
Well, it's just a suggestion.

36:15.760 --> 36:16.920
No.

36:17.040 --> 36:18.520
No, that's always
been Rita's territory.

36:18.640 --> 36:20.560
Probably best you
leave it to her then.

36:20.680 --> 36:21.600
Maybe so, Phineas.

36:21.720 --> 36:23.560
Maybe so.

