37:23.920 --> 37:25.320
in his truck
sometimes, which is how

37:25.440 --> 37:28.800
I know that all the
power that goes to there

37:28.920 --> 37:30.240
comes through here.

37:30.360 --> 37:32.400
And no power means nogame for the rugby heads.

37:32.520 --> 37:34.440
BERT: Well, they've probablygot backup generators and stuff.

37:34.560 --> 37:38.600
But yeah, for a while, a lotof pissed off rugby heads.

37:38.720 --> 37:39.560
Are you game?

37:39.680 --> 37:40.440
Hell yeah!

37:44.360 --> 37:46.200
This is mindless
vandalism, eh?

37:46.320 --> 37:48.080
But for a good cause.

37:48.200 --> 37:49.160
You think the game's started?

37:51.760 --> 37:52.920
Yep.

37:53.040 --> 37:53.800
Do it.

38:03.400 --> 38:04.240
Yeah!

38:04.360 --> 38:05.760
Woo!

38:05.880 --> 38:09.720
