his crew need a hand?

39:33.200 --> 39:35.640
[laughs] I'm sure Dave
can look after himself.

39:38.360 --> 39:39.200
Hey!

39:39.320 --> 39:40.080
Stop!

39:40.200 --> 39:41.160
