39:41.280 --> 39:42.640
Oy!

39:42.760 --> 39:45.080
Hey!

39:45.200 --> 39:51.440
[grunts] [grunts]

39:51.560 --> 39:55.200
You know, I'll be happywhen this bloody tour is over.

39:55.320 --> 39:57.120
Except if our Japie friends
leave without us having

39:57.240 --> 39:58.080
relieved them of their money.

39:58.200 --> 39:59.000
Don't gotta remind me.

39:59.120 --> 39:59.880
Fucking Des.

40:00.000 --> 40:01.360
[sirens]

40:01.480 --> 40:02.880
Oh, well.

40:03.000 --> 40:04.120
At least there's alwayssomeone worse off than we are.

40:07.840 --> 40:10.200
Where is Rocky's
fish place from here?

