41:45.160 --> 41:46.200
Wolf, don't be a smart ass.

41:46.320 --> 41:47.200
It was a job.

41:47.320 --> 41:48.800
Which you were told not to do!

41:48.920 --> 41:50.160
For your Dally mates!

41:50.280 --> 41:51.240
[MUSIC - TH' DUDES, "THAT LOOK IN YOUR EYES"]

41:51.360 --> 41:52.320
